  <Heading title="The Process" subtitle="" />

  <Heading3
    title="1. Designing the Interactive Lead Magnet (Engagement UX)"
    subtitle=`I designed and developed a highly interactive 3D web experience to capture user interest. Using Three.js, I built smooth card-flip mechanics that feel tactile and engaging. When a user interacts, the frontend hits an OpenAI endpoint to fetch a dynamically generated, personalized reading, converting a simple UI interaction into a high-value content delivery system.`
  />

